     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d255n2-ptr" id="PJA04d255n2">2</a>
      
   <p>Capt. Joseph White, commander of the sloop <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Revenge</span> (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ William Bell Clark, William James Morgan (from vol. 5), and others, eds., &lt;i&gt;Naval Documents of the American Revolution&lt;/i&gt;, Washington, 1964- ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Naval Docs. Amer. Rev.</span></span>, 6:78).</p>

     </div>
