   <p>Capt. Jeremiah OBrien, commander of the <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Machias Liberty</span>, a schooner owned by the state (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ William Bell Clark, William James Morgan (from vol. 5), and others, eds., &lt;i&gt;Naval Documents of the American Revolution&lt;/i&gt;, Washington, 1964- ]">same</span>).</p>

